dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Africa
dct_description_sm: Running title in margin: Library atlas of the world. [Africa.]. 91-92. Relief shown by hachures. Inset maps: Canal of Suez. Scale [ca. 1:1,100,000] -- Cape Verde Islands -- Cargados Carayos Islands, Mascarene Islands. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912. Historic Maps copy 2 shows railroad lines.
